Invocation Name: destination coimbatore
des: Destination Coimbatore is a local guide which recommends you the local hotels and attractions in Coimbatore.You can ask for the hotels and it's locations as well as you can ask for attractions or the places to be visited in Coimbatore.You can check the weather in Coimbatore before going out.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
